Wake up, wake up!

21
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:12,590
What are you doing, Chu Xiuming?!

22
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:15,100
Are you taking advantage of me since I'm drunk?

23
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:18,890
What did you do to me? Tell me!

24
00:02:19,550 --> 00:02:22,120
Don't misunderstand. You were drowning just now.

25
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:25,260
I was forced by the situation to do whatever it took to save you.

26
00:02:25,260 --> 00:02:27,110
Who would know anyways?

27
00:02:27,110 --> 00:02:30,040
No one else knows about the divorce letter you wrote me.

28
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:33,440
So what if you did anything to me?

29
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:37,950
Chu Xiuming, believe me when I say

30
00:02:37,950 --> 00:02:40,580
that I am going to telling everyone everything once I get back to the barracks.

31
00:02:40,580 --> 00:02:42,610
I want all the soldiers to know just what sort of person you are.

32
00:02:42,610 --> 00:02:44,110
You–!

33
00:02:49,700 --> 00:02:51,920
Can't you be like all the other ladies from respectable families

34
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:52,870
and be a little more reserved?

35
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:55,360
How am I not reserved?

36
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:58,740
I indeed don't behave like a lady from a respectable family. Sorry to disappoint.

37
00:02:58,740 --> 00:03:01,650
Aren't you the one who forced me to be like this?

38
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:05,010
You're the one who caused me to be homeless.

39
00:03:05,950 --> 00:03:10,490
I can't stay at the manor anymore, and now I can't stay at the barracks either.

40
00:03:10,490 --> 00:03:13,260
Did you think I could just return to my parents' home once you wrote the divorce letter?

41
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:15,620
If my mother were to find out...

42
00:03:18,070 --> 00:03:20,270
That's right.

43
00:03:20,270 --> 00:03:25,850
How heartbroken would my mother be if she found out?

44
00:03:26,450 --> 00:03:30,080
Then if my royal father found out, he would probably be very disappointed in me.

45
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:32,540
If my sisters knew about this,

46
00:03:32,540 --> 00:03:36,360
they would just mock and bully me even more.

47
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:42,480
What would everyone in the manor think of me if they knew?

48
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,910
I've come such a long way to marry you.

49
00:03:49,690 --> 00:03:52,990
You're the only person I can rely on,

50
00:03:52,990 --> 00:03:56,120
but why are you always bullying me?

51
00:03:56,850 --> 00:03:59,830
You said you would divorce me and then you did.

52
00:04:00,630 --> 00:04:02,840
You should at least give me a reason.

53
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,780
Why?

54
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:16,070
The divorce letter is written, I won't take it back.

55
00:04:17,450 --> 00:04:19,510
If you're afraid to return home,

56
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:22,170
I can accompany you there and personally explain the situation to your parents.

57
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:24,130
and personally explain the situation to your parents.

58
00:04:24,130 --> 00:04:25,840
This entire matter was my fault.

59
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,780
It has nothing to do with you.

60
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:32,920
You're only saying this to pacify me.

61
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:35,070
Did you think I would believe you?

62
00:04:35,070 --> 00:04:38,520
I, Chu Xiuming promise to accede to any request you make,

63
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:40,910
as long as I am able to fulfill it.

64
00:04:40,910 --> 00:04:42,110
Are you serious?

65
00:04:42,110 --> 00:04:45,650
Yes. I promise you.

66
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,750
It'll be dark soon.

67
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,660
We must return back to camp.

68
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:59,940
I can't move. I need you to piggyback me down the mountain.

