89
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:48,040
General.

90
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:35,400
Even though Miss has been persistent this whole time and hasn't been able to adjust,

91
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:38,400
she isn't one to concede easily when she's bullied.

92
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:42,100
But then again, I'm not at her side this time around.

93
00:07:42,100 --> 00:07:45,220
I wonder if she's doing all right.

94
00:07:49,210 --> 00:07:53,370
How do I solve this worry? The only way is by eating my fill.

95
00:07:53,370 --> 00:07:56,270
I should fill up my stomach before taking any action.

96
00:07:56,270 --> 00:07:58,970
I just can't look after her anymore.

97
00:08:09,010 --> 00:08:11,060
Aunt Qing Qiu. Are you making steamed buns?

98
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:12,350
Please hurry, please hurry.

99
00:08:12,350 --> 00:08:14,020
How does this look like dough for making steamed buns?

100
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:16,330
I'm making longevity noodles for the General. 
 <i>(Longevity noodles (寿面) symbolise longevity and can always be found on the banquet table during important celebrations.)</i>

101
00:08:16,330 --> 00:08:18,730
Longevity noodles? It's the General's birthday?

102
00:08:18,730 --> 00:08:21,010
Of course. His birthday is on the 8th of this month.

103
00:08:21,010 --> 00:08:22,460
The General isn't returning to the manor this year.

104
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:24,570
All the staff in the manor have to do their best,

105
00:08:24,570 --> 00:08:26,690
so I decided to make some longevity noodles for him to bring back to the barracks.

106
00:08:26,690 --> 00:08:28,660
The noodles will be brought back to the barracks?

107
00:08:29,610 --> 00:08:32,760
Aunt Qing Qiu, I'll bring it to the barracks for you.

108
00:08:33,940 --> 00:08:37,560
The way to the barracks is very bumpy. You're only a young lass, I'd feel sorry towards you.

109
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:39,040
What's there to be sorry for?

110
00:08:39,040 --> 00:08:42,070
I'm quite thick-skinned and I'm not afraid. I'll go.

111
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:44,580
If that's the case...

112
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:46,840
Then let me thank you first.

113
00:08:47,580 --> 00:08:50,110
Were you looking for me? What's the matter?

114
00:08:50,110 --> 00:08:51,490
I'm... Hungry.

115
00:08:51,490 --> 00:08:55,270
- I'll make whatever you wish to eat after I'm done with these longevity noodles. 
 - All right!

116
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:57,410
Aunt Qing Qiu, I'll go ahead and prepare the fire first.

117
00:08:57,410 --> 00:08:59,340
Wonderful!

118
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:08,370
I'll finally be able to visit Miss!

119
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,470
Isn't this Chu Xiuming's tent?

120
00:09:30,260 --> 00:09:32,870
I actually fell asleep here?

121
00:09:48,050 --> 00:09:51,770
I'm... Sorry about yesterday. I'd had too much to drink.

122
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:02,410
It's hangover soup. Drink it up quickly.

123
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:04,010
It'll soothe your stomach.

124
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:08,140
Doesn't that mean everyone already knows that I'd gotten drunk last night?

125
00:10:08,140 --> 00:10:11,610
Wouldn't they also find out that you'd covered up for me even though I'd violated martial law?

126
00:10:11,610 --> 00:10:15,080
Don't worry. I especially boiled this for you myself.

127
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,850
No one found out.

128
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:21,910
Drink it. I'll be leaving now.

129
00:10:23,940 --> 00:10:26,200
Where... Are you going?

130
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:29,060
The soldiers are going to do some farming on the fields today.

131
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:31,260
You should remain here and have a good rest.

132
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,980
Chu Xiuming...

133
00:11:02,900 --> 00:11:04,400
-Rou Rou.
-Auntie Qing Qiu!

134
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:07,270
Here. There are forty mantou inside, take it.

135
00:11:07,270 --> 00:11:08,770
Our Lady gets hungry easily.

136
00:11:08,770 --> 00:11:11,750
During crucial times, it can help save her life!

137
00:11:11,750 --> 00:11:14,090
You might choke our Miss to death!

138
00:11:14,090 --> 00:11:18,030
Alright, Auntie Qing Qiu, fine. Choking to death is better than starving to death.

139
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:19,260
That's right, that's right.

140
00:11:19,260 --> 00:11:22,960
Rou Rou. This is the cape I personally made.

141
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:26,780
The military camps are in a bad environment. I'm afraid Lady will get cold.

142
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:30,220
She can use this to fight the cold. To make she won't freeze to lose an arm or a leg.

143
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:33,600
Wearing a fur cape in this weather...?

144
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,750
A....alright.

145
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:39,660
Rou Rou. If Lady gets sick, she must take medicine!

146
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:42,880
Can she take medicine at will like this?

147
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:44,320
F-f-fine.

148
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,970
Having it is better than not.

149
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:52,270
The moon wax and wane, people faces disaster and good fortune.

150
00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:55,340
My pitiful Lady!

151
00:11:55,340 --> 00:11:58,540
Shut up! Miss isn't dead yet!

152
00:11:59,170 --> 00:12:03,000
Having to go to war, I'm afraid she will...!

153
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,960
Auntie Qing Qiu!

154
00:12:06,700 --> 00:12:10,700
-Good luck to her, good luck to her!
-Good luck!

155
00:12:14,170 --> 00:12:16,200
- Rou Rou! 
 - What is it?

156
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,630
Rou Rou!

157
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:21,110
Look, you have so much stuff. Take me with you!

158
00:12:21,110 --> 00:12:25,160
I can help you carry things and take care of Lady. Okay?

159
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,890
This wouldn't be very proper, Xiao Cong.

160
00:12:26,890 --> 00:12:31,330
If we both leave, Auntie Qing Qiu can't keep up with the manor.

161
00:12:31,330 --> 00:12:33,480
It won't be good if General finds out.

162
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:36,800
Take me with you! I just want to see him...

163
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,800
See who?

164
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:41,230
Her Ladyship! Of course, it's Her Ladyship.

165
00:12:41,230 --> 00:12:44,920
Don't worry! I will take good care of our Miss!

166
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:47,260
- I. 
 - Let's go!

167
00:12:47,260 --> 00:12:49,980
Hurry and go back! Go on!

168
00:12:56,950 --> 00:13:02,010
My Lieutenant General... this is the 17th day since you left the manor!

169
00:13:02,010 --> 00:13:05,100
I miss you so much!

170
00:13:05,100 --> 00:13:08,140
My heart feels awful!

171
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:12,070
I would turn into the Amah Rock, no matter the blowing wind or the burning sun,

172
00:13:12,070 --> 00:13:15,230
I would always wait for you to come back here.

173
00:13:16,160 --> 00:13:20,900
Lieutenant General! When will you come back?

174
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:24,380
Miss! Miss!

175
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:27,740
-Miss!
-Rou Rou!

176
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:32,140
I miss you so much! I'm so glad you're still alive!

177
00:13:32,140 --> 00:13:35,690
I came to join the army, not to die! Don't curse me!

178
00:13:35,690 --> 00:13:38,140
Look! Aren't I doing just fine?

179
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:40,100
Rou Rou, why did you come here?

180
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:45,300
I used the excuse of bringing longevity noodles to the General to bring you supplies!

181
00:13:45,300 --> 00:13:48,080
Longevity noodles? It's the General's birthday?

182
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:51,140
It's today. You didn't know?

183
00:13:52,090 --> 00:13:55,040
Rou Rou. You came just in time!

184
00:13:56,600 --> 00:14:00,130
It's the General's birthday! We must celebrate it properly!

185
00:14:02,460 --> 00:14:05,980
Miss. You've only been here for a few days.

186
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:10,410
Why has your mood completely changed? That's not what you said when you came here.

187
00:14:11,090 --> 00:14:16,340
This, suddenly becoming a lackey! And even preparing a birthday gift for the general.

188
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:19,430
Rou Rou! You weren't here.

189
00:14:19,430 --> 00:14:20,880
You really don't know.

190
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:27,170
This devil... is already deeply in love with me!

191
00:14:28,670 --> 00:14:33,970
It's just, he has to keep face and won't tell me directly!

192
00:14:33,970 --> 00:14:35,620
Really?

193
00:14:37,430 --> 00:14:42,300
Since he loves me so much, I can only help him out and give him a chance!

194
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:46,240
At the same time, I will let him know how good I am to him!

195
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:52,900
But...in the  military camp,

196
00:14:52,900 --> 00:14:56,570
I can't make a very proper birthday gift.

197
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:08,290
Hey, Bao Zitou!

198
00:15:08,290 --> 00:15:10,370
Bao Zitou!

199
00:15:11,430 --> 00:15:13,250
This person...!

200
00:15:24,330 --> 00:15:28,090
Bao Zitou! Is this just to scare people?

201
00:15:28,090 --> 00:15:32,450
Your blade is much lighter than the General's sword! Even I can pick it up!

202
00:15:32,450 --> 00:15:34,190
Bao Zitou!

203
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:38,180
L-l-lady!

204
00:15:38,180 --> 00:15:40,960
Let me ask you. Everyone is working outside.

205
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:43,160
Why are you sleeping here?

206
00:15:43,160 --> 00:15:47,780
I-i-i-i-i didn't fall asleep, Lady. General told me to watch the camp.

207
00:15:47,780 --> 00:15:51,660
Fine. I need something from you.

208
00:15:51,660 --> 00:15:56,070
Today, I need to prepare for the General's birthday. I need your help for something.

209
00:15:56,070 --> 00:15:58,170
Go ahead, Lady.

210
00:15:58,170 --> 00:16:01,040
Can you let me borrow some military explosives?

211
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:04,630
In Rui Royal Manor, I once saw a method of making fireworks with explosives.

212
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:09,300
I want to make beautiful fireworks for the General's birthday!

213
00:16:09,300 --> 00:16:11,290
You must not, you must not, Lady!

214
00:16:11,290 --> 00:16:15,120
Military explosives are given by the royal court! It is a terrible crime to use it for personal reasons!

215
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:18,340
Even if the General asked me for it, I wouldn't give it to him.

216
00:16:18,340 --> 00:16:22,760
Not just the General, even if my own father came over, I wouldn't agree.

217
00:16:23,400 --> 00:16:26,070
It's fine, why are you bringing up your father?

218
00:16:26,070 --> 00:16:28,530
- I... 
 -Go back to sleep!

219
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:36,250
I didn't fall asleep. I'm watching the camp.

220
00:16:36,250 --> 00:16:38,170
Oh. Go ahead.

221
00:16:38,170 --> 00:16:41,040
Hey! No! I...

222
00:16:41,970 --> 00:16:43,290
Here.

223
00:16:43,290 --> 00:16:45,120
Thank you Lady.

224
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:47,000
Is this just to scare people?

225
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:56,490
Lieutenant General!

226
00:16:57,460 --> 00:16:59,240
Please go ahead, Lady.

227
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:03,160
I have a request for you. Today is the General's birthday.

228
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:06,830
I want to prepare a fancy banquet for him, and give him a surprise!

229
00:17:06,830 --> 00:17:10,200
Lady, I already heard from Bao Zitou you want to borrow some military explosives.

230
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:13,700
I cannot help you. Besides, a banquet is too wasteful.

231
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:16,910
Given the current military supplies, I'm afraid it can't be done.

232
00:17:16,910 --> 00:17:18,530
Alright then.

233
00:17:18,530 --> 00:17:22,100
Then is there anything else that can surprise the General?

234
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:25,390
General usually doesn't like to celebrate his birthday.

235
00:17:25,390 --> 00:17:29,750
Lady, I think your presence here this year is his best birthday surprise.

236
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:32,640
Then I will leave now.

237
00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:40,850
Miss...it seems like Lieutenant General won't help us either.

238
00:17:40,850 --> 00:17:42,770
What do we do?

239
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:45,820
